---
layout : layouts/home.njk
---
<section class="bg-[#112C40]">
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2">
    <div class="py-11 px-6 flex flex-col items-start justify-center">
      <div class="text-white text-5xl mb-9">YOUR
        <span class="text-accent-500">TRUSTED</span>
        ADVISOR</div>
      <div class="text-white leading-normal text-2xl mb-9">
        You are stuck or need an assessment? We help you get things under control before, during or even after a ServiceNow implementation.
      </div>
      <button class="group relative btn overflow-hidden rounded-lg bg-accent-500 text-lg shadow border-solid border-2 border-accent-500">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 w-0 bg-accent-400 transition-all duration-[250ms] ease-out group-hover:w-full"></div>
        <span class="relative text-black ">Let WORK Flow</span>
      </button>
    </div>

    <div class="">
      <img src="/assets/bjorn.png" alt="" class="w-full h-full object-cover max-h-[680px]"/>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="border-b border-gray-200">
  <div class="container py-11 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3">
    <div class="flex items-center justify-center">
      <img src="/assets/icons/show.svg" alt="" class="mr-6"/>
      Show Me
    </div>
    <div class="flex items-center justify-center">
      <img src="/assets/icons/contact.svg" alt="" class="mr-6"/>
      Contact Us
    </div>
    <div class="flex items-center justify-center">
      <img src="/assets/icons/discover.svg" alt="" class="mr-6"/>
      View Customer Stories
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <div class="container grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 py-11 gap-8">
    <div>
      <img src="/assets/illustration-1.png" alt=""/>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-col justify-center items-start">
      <div class="mb-6 text-4xl">The platform of platforms</div>
      <div class="leading-normal mb-6 text-xl">
        Behind every great experience is a great workflow. As the foundation for all digital workflows, the Now Platform
                                connects people, functions, and systems across your organization.
      </div>
      <button class="group relative btn overflow-hidden rounded-lg bg-white text-lg shadow border-solid border-2 border-accent-500 ">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 w-0 bg-accent-500 transition-all duration-[250ms] ease-out group-hover:w-full"></div>
        <span class="relative text-black ">Explore Platform</span>
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
